Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!\NDidn't Curly Cook come out with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to chase\Nafter me no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about that huge zombie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but taking you down is the only way\Nto recover everyone's shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I am the last one laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go elsewhere... and hold\Nthe ceremony... one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my quiet bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-We've got a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Our wanted posters are\Na-attached to Zombie Luffy's arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Straw Hat Crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, Luffy! Are you going\Nto crush your own crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must have issued the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the real Luffy is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we take that monster down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Is the Enemy! The Ultimate Zombie\Nvs. the Straw Hat Crew!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What is that? Its face freaks me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's literally a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp! That you down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I thought I\Nheard someone say my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zoro! Why are you on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! And Brook's okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, it looks like we can\Ncheck the skeleton off our list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too soon to check Nami-chan off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, move your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why in the world are you\Ngetting in our way, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff it! What's "nice" about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! That is such a \Nbirdbrained thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound just like Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to pick a \Nfight with that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that moronic cook manage to save Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in hotter water than the girlie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Crap! This looks really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had assumed they were only \Ninterested in our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like all they care\Nabout now is Luffy's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! I'm scared! I \Ncan't fight that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I should lend him a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We should leave this to Sanji\Nso we don't trip him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He should be able\Nto escape without too much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't that giant recognize him\Nfrom the wanted poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt the beast will \Nsimply let him walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a lot to learn, Robin-kun!\NThat's just the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he'll recognize Sanji based off
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the composite sketch on the wanted poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Sanji doesn't look anything\Nlike the picture on his wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bingo!\N--I see. You have a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you look just like the\Npicture on the wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What looks the same?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What," huh? Your whole face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, aren't you one of the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat! That shadow got in the way again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! This is a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally got you cornered!\NSay your prayers, Giant Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be the one saying your prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're wasting time with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your combat skills are being used\Nto wipe out your crew, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! My crew won't go down that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? Then I'd better make\Na break for it before you do me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-sama, we've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-sama, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being obnoxious,\Nyou poor excuse for a penguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, stinky old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! This is no time for\Narguing amongst ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to bicker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're following Hogback-sama's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it, you lousy bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback-sama would never order \Nyou to do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take out the pests!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take out the pest!\N--You're the pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're a lost cause...\N--You are such a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! That still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk tried to make a fool of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not about to pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't collapse until this\Nevent of a lifetime is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's resume the\Nwedding ceremony. Kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally get to kiss her this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Absalom-sama might\Nknow where Moria-sama went.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here I go!\N--Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that for, you perverted beast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He insulted him! He slammed \Nhim with an insult!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Now we're in for a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hildon, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's surprisingly calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm trying to find Moria-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see for yourself? He isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you get\Nsomeone else to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the intrusion. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, Hildon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call me a "perverted beast"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took that long to sink in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Giant Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! It's that stupid shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he really let me have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria-sama, I have news that\NI'd like to report right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hildon? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it would appear the ship\Nis moving in an unfortunate direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll run into trouble if it\Ncontinues on its current course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? If that's the case,\Ndo something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Later!\N--B-But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way! Move it! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn twerp's quickly darting every which way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, all that did was make a dust cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of Luffy's moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he extend his arms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a rubber man now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-His arm didn't extend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with power and reach \Nlike that, who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that freakishly huge \Nbody isn't just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one direct hit could\Ndo some serious damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars... I've heard that \Nname somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he be the legendary Continent Puller\Nfrom ancient times, the Devil Oars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd explain it. It sounds like\NLuffy's zombie isn't a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collier Frit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stinking fast for a behemoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got ya, puny pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! He's gonna get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that monster gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, puny pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Bird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is the black-haired woman\Nand the reindeer eating cotton candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's headed our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Franky, lure him over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off the roof, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One Gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Two Gorilla Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Volcano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's dead if he falls from up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chew on this, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so nimble! He dodged again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he up to this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! He'll die if he hits the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs! Spider Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I survived? Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this! You're still a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Salt Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for his massive body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy Gong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know any of you losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Moria-sama's servant, Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ab-sama! Forget that woman and pucker up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn when to quit! I won't kiss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then marry me!\N--That isn't happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then kiss me!\N--Are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit! You made her wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're Going Down, Absalom!!\NNami's Lightning Attack of Friendship!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
